<p style=";text-align:left;background:rgb(252,252,252)">
    <span style=";font-family:宋体;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:宋体">（</span>6<span style="font-family:宋体">）</span><span style="font-family:Arial">1127</span><span style="font-family:宋体">年赵构称帝，是为宋高宗 &nbsp;南宋 &nbsp;</span></span>
