    <span style=";font-family:宋体;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:宋体">（</span>8<span style="font-family:宋体">）</span><span style="font-family:Arial">1271</span><span style="font-family:宋体">年忽必烈改国号为元，</span><span style="font-family:Arial">1276</span><span style="font-family:宋体">年南宋灭亡 </span></span>
</p>
<p style=";text-align:left;background:rgb(252,252,252)">
    <span style=";font-family:宋体;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:宋体">（</span>9<span style="font-family:宋体">）元朝是我国疆域最辽阔的朝代 &nbsp;</span></span>
</p>
<p style=";text-align:left;background:rgb(252,252,252)">
    <span style=";font-family:宋体;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:宋体">（</span>10<span style="font-family:宋体">）行省制和宣政院（管佛教和藏族事务） </span></span>
</p>
<p style=";text-align:left;background:rgb(252,252,252)">
