    <span style=";font-family:宋体;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:宋体">（</span>1<span style="font-family:宋体">）</span><span style="font-family:Arial">1368</span><span style="font-family:宋体">年朱元璋在应天称帝，明朝建立 </span></span>
</p>
