    <span style=";font-family:宋体;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:宋体">（</span>2<span style="font-family:宋体">）明朝专制统治加强； </span></span>
</p>
<p style=";text-align:left;background:rgb(252,252,252)">
    <span style=";font-family:宋体;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:宋体">（</span>3<span style="font-family:宋体">）郑和下西洋 &nbsp;</span></span>
</p>
<p style=";text-align:left;background:rgb(252,252,252)">
    <span style=";font-family:宋体;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:宋体">（</span>4<span style="font-family:宋体">）李自成农民起义 </span></span>
</p>
<p style=";text-align:left;background:rgb(252,252,252)">
    <span style=";font-family:宋体;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:宋体">（</span>5<span style="font-family:宋体">）</span><span style="font-family:Arial">1644</span><span style="font-family:宋体">年明覆灭 &nbsp;</span></span>
