<p style=";text-align:left;background:rgb(252,252,252)">
    <span style=";font-family:宋体;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:宋体">（</span>6<span style="font-family:宋体">）</span><span style="font-family:Arial">1644</span><span style="font-family:宋体">年清军攻占北京，顺治逐步统一全国 </span></span>
</p>
<p style=";text-align:left;background:rgb(252,252,252)">
    <strong><span style=";font-family:宋体;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-weight:bold;font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:宋体">三、中国近代史</span></span></strong><span style=";font-family:宋体;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:12px">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>
</p>
<p style=";text-align:left;background:rgb(252,252,252)">
    <span style=";font-family:宋体;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:12px">1.<span style="font-family:宋体">鸦片战争：</span><span style="font-family:Arial">1840</span><span style="font-family:宋体">年鸦片战争；</span><span style="font-family:Arial">1841</span><span style="font-family:宋体">年英军占领香港；</span><span style="font-family:Arial">1842</span><span style="font-family:宋体">年签订《南京条约》 </span></span>
</p>
<p style=";text-align:left;background:rgb(252,252,252)">
    <span style=";font-family:宋体;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:12px">2.<span style="font-family:宋体">太平天国：</span><span style="font-family:Arial">1851</span><span style="font-family:宋体">年洪秀全发动金田起义；</span><span style="font-family:Arial">1853</span><span style="font-family:宋体">年攻占南京 </span></span>
