</p>
<p style=";text-align:left;background:rgb(252,252,252)">
    <strong><span style=";font-family:宋体;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-weight:bold;font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:宋体">第二节：世界历史</span> &nbsp;</span></strong>
</p>
<p style=";text-align:left;background:rgb(252,252,252)">
    <strong><span style=";font-family:宋体;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-weight:bold;font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:宋体">一、古代史</span></span></strong><span style=";font-family:宋体;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:12px">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>
</p>
<p style=";text-align:left;background:rgb(252,252,252)">
    <span style=";font-family:宋体;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:12px">1<span style="font-family:宋体">、</span></span><strong><span style=";font-family:宋体;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-weight:bold;font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:宋体">埃及</span></span></strong><span style=";font-family:宋体;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:宋体">是世界上</span></span><strong><span style=";font-family:宋体;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-weight:bold;font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:宋体">最早</span></span></strong><span style=";font-family:宋体;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:宋体">的</span></span><strong><span style=";font-family:宋体;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-weight:bold;font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:宋体">奴隶制国家</span></span></strong><span style=";font-family:宋体;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:宋体">；</span></span>
</p>
<p style=";text-align:left;background:rgb(252,252,252)">
