</p>
<p style=";text-align:left;background:rgb(252,252,252)">
    <span style=";font-family:宋体;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:12px">7<span style="font-family:宋体">、</span></span><strong><span style=";font-family:宋体;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-weight:bold;font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:宋体">斯巴达</span></span></strong><span style=";font-family:宋体;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:宋体">：贵族军事专制统治；</span></span><strong><span style=";font-family:宋体;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-weight:bold;font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:宋体">雅典</span></span></strong><span style=";font-family:宋体;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:宋体">：奴隶主共和制</span> </span>
</p>
