</p>
<p style=";text-align:left;background:rgb(252,252,252)">
    <span style=";font-family:宋体;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:12px">9<span style="font-family:宋体">、</span></span><strong><span style=";font-family:宋体;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-weight:bold;font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:宋体">罗马</span></span></strong><span style=";font-family:宋体;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:宋体">奴隶制共和国</span> &nbsp;</span>
