<p style=";text-align:left;background:rgb(252,252,252)">
    <span style=";font-family:宋体;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:12px">10<span style="font-family:宋体">、</span></span><strong><span style="text-decoration:underline;"><span style=";font-family:宋体;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-weight:bold;text-underline:single;font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:宋体">斯巴达克起义：古代历史上规模最大的一次奴隶起义</span></span></span></strong><span style=";font-family:宋体;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:12px">&nbsp;</span>
</p>
<p style=";text-align:left;background:rgb(252,252,252)">
    <span style=";font-family:宋体;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:12px">11<span style="font-family:宋体">、</span></span><strong><span style="text-decoration:underline;"><span style=";font-family:宋体;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-weight:bold;text-underline:single;font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:宋体">基督教</span></span></span></strong><span style=";font-family:宋体;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:宋体">的兴起：</span>1<span style="font-family:宋体">世纪 &nbsp;</span></span>
</p>
<p style=";text-align:left;background:rgb(252,252,252)">
    <span style=";font-family:宋体;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:12px">12<span style="font-family:宋体">、</span></span><strong><span style="text-decoration:underline;"><span style=";font-family:宋体;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-weight:bold;text-underline:single;font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:宋体">文艺复兴三杰</span></span></span></strong><span style=";font-family:宋体;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:宋体">：</span></span><strong><span style=";font-family:宋体;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-weight:bold;font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:宋体">但丁《神曲》</span> <span style="font-family:宋体">、比特拉克《歌集》；薄伽丘《十日谈》</span></span></strong><span style=";font-family:宋体;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:12px">&nbsp;</span>
</p>
<p style=";text-align:left;background:rgb(252,252,252)">
    <span style=";font-family:宋体;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:12px">13<span style="font-family:宋体">、绘画三杰：</span></span><strong><span style=";font-family:宋体;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-weight:bold;font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:宋体">达芬奇、米开朗琪罗、拉斐尔</span></span></strong><span style=";font-family:宋体;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:12px">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>
</p>
<p style=";text-align:left;background:rgb(252,252,252)">
