</p>
<p style=";text-align:left;background:rgb(252,252,252)">
    <strong><span style=";font-family:宋体;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-weight:bold;font-size:12px">&nbsp;</span></strong>
</p>
<p style=";text-align:left;background:rgb(252,252,252)">
    <strong><span style=";font-family:宋体;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-weight:bold;font-size:12px">&nbsp;</span></strong>
</p>
<p style=";text-align:left;background:rgb(252,252,252)">
    <strong><span style=";font-family:宋体;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-weight:bold;font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:宋体">二、近代史：</span> &nbsp;</span></strong>
</p>
<p style=";text-align:left;background:rgb(252,252,252)">
    <strong><span style=";font-family:宋体;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-weight:bold;font-size:12px">1<span style="font-family:宋体">、英国资产阶级革命</span></span></strong><span style=";font-family:宋体;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:宋体">：</span> &nbsp;</span>
</p>
<p style=";text-align:left;background:rgb(252,252,252)">
    <span style=";font-family:宋体;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:宋体">导火索：</span>1638<span style="font-family:宋体">年苏格兰人民起义 &nbsp;</span></span>
