<p style=";text-align:left;background:rgb(252,252,252)">
    <strong><span style=";font-family:宋体;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-weight:bold;font-size:12px"><span style="font-family:宋体">五、科举考试：</span></span></strong><span style=";font-family:宋体;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:12px">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>
</p>
<p style=";text-align:left;background:rgb(252,252,252)">
    <span style=";font-family:宋体;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:12px">1<span style="font-family:宋体">、童试：皆可参考，合格即为秀才、生员； &nbsp;</span></span>
</p>
<p style=";text-align:left;background:rgb(252,252,252)">
    <span style=";font-family:宋体;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:12px">2<span style="font-family:宋体">、乡试：秀才参考，合格即为举人，第一名为解元，其他为举人； &nbsp;</span></span>
</p>
<p style=";text-align:left;background:rgb(252,252,252)">
    <span style=";font-family:宋体;color:rgb(51,51,51);font-size:12px">3<span style="font-family:宋体">、会试：举人和监生参考，合格即为贡生，第一名称为会元，其余皆为贡生； </span></span>
</p>
